#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:25
msgid "Template Titles"
msgstr "Sjabloontitels"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:27
msgid ""
"**Template Titles** (not to be confused with Title Templates) allow you to"
" create a template for other titles in your project. You create the templa"
"te title with the settings that all or a considerable number of the titles"
" in the project should have, and then base subsequent titles on that templ"
"ate. If you decide to change the look of your titles, you only need to cha"
"nge the template title, and the titles based on this template will automat"
"ically update to reflect any formatting changes you made to the template t"
"itle. Apart from that, template titles behave like any other title clip."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:31
msgid "Create a Template Title"
msgstr "Een titelsjabloon aanmaken"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:33
msgid ""
"Create a new title clip like normal, add any objects you need, and any sta"
"tic text. Create a new text field, and enter :code:`%s`. This will be repl"
"aced later with text you specify for each title you add to the project bas"
"ed on this template. Adjust the font attributes, alignment, shadow, and th"
"e :ref:`typewriter<title-text_typewriter>` effect as required. If the titl"
"e needs :doc:`animation</titles_and_graphics/graphics_and_animations/title"
"_scrolling>`, you can create that, too."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:35
msgid ""
"Instead of simply clicking on :guilabel:`Create title`, click on |document"
"-save-as|\\ :guilabel:`Save As`, or press :kbd:`Ctrl+S`, and save the temp"
"late title. Give it a meaningful name for better recognizeability."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:39
msgid "Use the Template Title"
msgstr "De titelsjabloon gebruiken"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:41
msgid ""
"In the Project Bin, click on |kdenlive-add-clip|\\ |go-down|\\ :guilabel:`"
"Add clip or folder` and select :guilabel:`Add Template Title`, or right-cl"
"ick on empty space in the Project Bin, and select :guilabel:`Add Template "
"Title`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:51
msgid "Adding a template title"
msgstr "Een sjabloontitel toevoegen"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:53
msgid ""
"Kdenlive opens a window with a drop-down list with all the title templates"
" and a preview area. Select the template you just created, or in case you "
"saved it elsewhere click the |document-open|\\ :guilabel:`Open file dialog"
"` icon, navigate to the respective folder, and open the :file:`.kdenliveti"
"tle` file from there."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:57
msgid ""
"Kdenlive added a new title clip to the Project Bin. Right-click this clip "
"in the Project Bin and select :guilabel:`Clip Properties`, or in case you "
"have the :guilabel:`Clip Properties` widget available, simply open it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:67
msgid "Using a template title"
msgstr "Een sjabloontitel gebruiken"

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:69
msgid ""
"Enter the text that this title should display into the text field in the d"
"ialog that appears."
msgstr ""
"Voer de tekst in die deze titel zou moeten tonen display in het tekstveld "
"in "
"de dialoog die verschijnt."

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:71
msgid ""
"You can change the :guilabel:`Duration` by ticking the box and entering a "
"new value (format is hh:mm:ss:ff)."
msgstr ""
"U kunt de :guilabel:`Tijdsduur` wijzigen door het vak te activeren en een "
"nieuwe waarde (formaat is hh:mm:ss:ff) in te voeren."

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:73
msgid ""
"You can edit the template by clicking on the :guilabel:`Edit Clip` button."
msgstr ""
"U kunt het sjabloon bewerken door te klikken op de knop :guilabel:`Clip "
"bewerken`."

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:75
msgid "Click on :guilabel:`Apply` to create or change this title clip."
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:79
msgid "Drag the title to the timeline."
msgstr "Sleep de titel naar de tijdlijn."

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:89
msgid "A template title at work"
msgstr ""

#: ../../titles_and_graphics/titles/title_template_titles.rst:91
msgid ""
"The :code:`%s` in the template will be replaced with the text that you ent"
"er in the :guilabel:`Text` field."
msgstr ""

